summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from the Union Trust Company, a corporation, to the City of Seattle, dated the 13th day of December, 1907, to All of Block fifteen (15); Lots four (4), five (5), six (6), ten (10), eleven (11) and twelve (12) in Block Twenty-six (26); Lots four (4), five (5), six (6), ten (10), eleven (11), and twelve (12) in Block Twenty-seven (27), all in Pike's Second Addition to Union City, now in the City of Seattle.
